data.description: Wonderful well-kept 3-bedroom brick home in a great area of Taylor, perfect for a young growing family!!!  Home features a dimensional roof, replacement windows, nice full eat-in kitchen with stone countertops, updated bath with a double sink and Corian countertops, glass block basement windows, newer hot water tank and partially finished basement......no worries about city inspections or having to make city repairs as the seller will be providing a Certificate of Occupancy at closing.
